{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/joomla-parameter/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Gibt es Einstellungen, die für alle Items deiner Komponente gelten und ein Anwender an seine Erfordernisse anpasst? In Joomla! gibt für diesen Zweck Parameter.</p>\n<p>Parameter gibt es für</p>\n<ul>\n<li>ein Item speziell,</li>\n<li>für die ganze Komponente und</li>\n<li>für einen Menüpunkt.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Wenn ein Parameter bei den drei Möglichkeiten gesetzt ist, dann gilt folgende Hierarchie:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Der Menüpunkt schlägt alles.</li>\n<li>Danach zieht der Parameter, der für das Item speziell gilt.</li>\n<li>Die niedrigst Priorität hat der Parameter, der für die ganze Komponente gilt.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Beim Menüpunkt hatten wir schon einen Parameter gesetzt und für die Komponente als Ganzes gibt es diesen in den Optionen. Das Item im Speziellen ist jetzt an der Reihe.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/53ac9/j4x22x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.46625766871166%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla! Published\"\n        title=\"Joomla! Published\"\n        src=\"/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/a6d36/j4x22x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/222b7/j4x22x1.png 163w,\n/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/ff46a/j4x22x1.png 325w,\n/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/a6d36/j4x22x1.png 650w,\n/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/e548f/j4x22x1.png 975w,\n/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/53ac9/j4x22x1.png 1287w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Für Ungeduldige</h2>\n<p>Sieh dir den geänderten Programmcode in der <a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18\">Diff-Ansicht</a> an und übernimm diese Änderungen in deine Entwicklungsversion.</p>\n<h2>Schritt für Schritt</h2>\n<h3>Neue Dateien</h3>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-61df23203c29920003ce39f96f2fb2f7\">src/administrator/components/com_foos/sql/updates/mysql/18.0.0.sql</a></h4>\n<h3>Geänderte Dateien</h3>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-9be56d6cedb2c832265e47642f0afb25\">src/administrator/components/com_foos/config.xml</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-262e27353fbe755d3813ea2df19cd0ed\">src/administrator/components/com_foos/forms/foo.xml</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-896f245bc8e493f91277fd33913ef974\">src/administrator/components/com_foos/sql/install.mysql.utf8.sql</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-19bf55010e1963bede0668355cebb307\">src/administrator/components/com_foos/src/Table/FooTable.php</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-c77adeff4ff9e321c996e0e12c54b656\">src/components/com_foos/src/View/Foo/HtmlView.php</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-a33732ebd6992540b8adca5615b51a1f\">src/components/com_foos/tmpl/foo/default.php</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h4><a href=\"https://github.com/astridx/boilerplate/compare/t17...t18#diff-35fa310ee8efa91ecb0e9f7c604d413f\">src/components/com_foos/tmpl/foo/default.xml</a></h4>\n<p><a href=\"\"></a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Teste deine Joomla-Komponente</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Installiere deine Komponente in Joomla! Version 4, um sie zu testen:</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Kopiere die Dateien im <code class=\"language-text\">administrator</code> Ordner in den <code class=\"language-text\">administrator</code> Ordner deiner Joomla! 4 Installation.<br>\nKopiere die Dateien im <code class=\"language-text\">components</code> Ordner in den <code class=\"language-text\">components</code> Ordner deiner Joomla! 4 Installation.<br>\nKopiere die Dateien im <code class=\"language-text\">media</code> Ordner in den <code class=\"language-text\">media</code> Ordner deiner Joomla! 4 Installation.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Die Datenbank ist geändert worden, so dass es erforderlich ist, sie zu aktualisieren. Öffne den Bereich <code class=\"language-text\">System | Information | Database</code>, wie in Teil 16 beschrieben. Wähle deine Komponente aus und klicke auf <code class=\"language-text\">Update Structure</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/53ac9/j4x16x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48.46625766871166%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla! Published\"\n        title=\"Joomla! Published\"\n        src=\"/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/a6d36/j4x16x1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/222b7/j4x16x1.png 163w,\n/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/ff46a/j4x16x1.png 325w,\n/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/a6d36/j4x16x1.png 650w,\n/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/e548f/j4x16x1.png 975w,\n/static/d2f2afde2cc7c1516e936433fa6ce907/53ac9/j4x16x1.png 1287w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Öffne die Ansicht deiner Komponente im Administrationsbereich. Beim Bearbeiten eines Items steht der Tabulator.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/01072d2ce06d9287c10dc7abbb5fa4c2/53ac9/j4x22x1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block